List the lead ids currently in the user's selection (the transient set that bulk operations like enrichment act on).

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} to verify the selection state before/after bulk ops if a composite call has misbehaved.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} in the normal flow — leadbay_enrich_titles manages selection lifecycle automatically (select → action → clear).
